释义：
make fun of 嘲笑
与表示“嘲笑”，“欺骗”的 make a fool of 具有相近的含义，make fun of 后面可以接 somebody 或 something。
例句：
You're making fun of me?
你在嘲笑我？
Don't make fun of me, okay?
别嘲笑我，行不？
You're making a fool of yourself.
你在自欺欺人。
对话：
A: It must be difficult to be a fat person.
做一个胖人肯定很不容易。
B: Many people make fun of fat people.
很多人嘲笑胖子。